explanations.description: Words or parts of words associated with the prefix "som-" or "son-" that appear in a variety of contexts, including geographical locations (e.g. Somalia, Somerville, Sonoma), names (e.g. Sommers), and terms related to the body (e.g. soma, somatic), as well as other miscellaneous words (e.g. somme, somers).
